---
title: Family-Style Chicken & Spinach Pasta Bake 2x the delicious servings!
description: Imagine this: tender pasta with garlicky bites of juicy chicken and earthy spinach folded into a velvety lemon-Parmesan cream sauce and baked to crispy and luscious perfection. Now imagine it’s on the table, family style, ready to feed the hungriest of eaters in no time at all. The time you’ll save making this big batch meal means that much more time to hang with the fam. It’s a homey, wholesome dinner idea that’s perfect for company or just the regulars (+ leftovers—hello lunch, tomorrow!).

This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.
